    Both centered, using the theme heading fonts.
    
    Cards:
    
    Below the heading, show a grid of authentication steps as cards.
    
    Each card is a block in the section. For every block I need:
    
    Icon image picker (small, gold line icons).
    
    Title text (short heading).
    
    Body text (2–3 lines).
    
    On desktop, layout the cards in a responsive grid that keeps everything centered. For 6 cards:
    
    First row: 4 cards
    
    Second row: 2 cards in the center
    
    On mobile, stack all cards vertically, centered, with good spacing between icon, title and body.
    
    Style:
    
    Icons centered above the title, around 48–64 px size.
    
    Titles in bold, body text in regular weight.
    
